// [FIXED] ‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏¥‡πà‡∏°‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ß‡∏à‡∏™‡∏≠‡∏ö‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏Ç‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≤‡πÄ‡∏û‡∏∑‡πà‡∏≠‡∏õ‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏±‡∏ô‡∏Ç‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏°‡∏π‡∏•‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏¢‡∏±‡∏á‡πÑ‡∏°‡πà‡∏ñ‡∏π‡∏Å Join
const requiredKeys = ['rules', 'events', 'stats', 'statTimes', 'kpis', 'uptime_results'];
const payloadOk = msg.payload && typeof msg.payload === 'object' && !Array.isArray(msg.payload);
