 * @param {*} v ‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏ï‡πâ‡∏≠‡∏á‡∏Å‡∏≤‡∏£‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏á
 * @returns {number|null}
 */
function toNum(v) {
    if (v === null || v === undefined) return null;
    const n = Number(v);
    return Number.isFinite(n) ? n : null;
}

/**
 * ‡∏î‡∏∂‡∏á‡∏Ñ‡πà‡∏≤‡∏à‡∏≤‡∏Å object ‡πÇ‡∏î‡∏¢‡πÉ‡∏ä‡πâ key ‡∏ó‡∏µ‡πà‡∏Å‡∏≥‡∏´‡∏ô‡∏î
 * @param {object} obj
 * @param {string[]} keys
 * @returns {*}
 */
function pick(obj, keys) {
    for (const k of keys) {
        if (obj?.[k] !== undefined && obj[k] !== null) {
            return obj[k];
        }
    }
    return undefined;
}

/**
 * ‡∏à‡∏±‡∏î‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö MAC address ‡πÉ‡∏´‡πâ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏°‡∏≤‡∏ï‡∏£‡∏ê‡∏≤‡∏ô
 * @param {string} s
 * @returns {string|undefined}
 */
function normMAC(s) {
    const hex = String(s || '').toUpperCase().replace(/[^0-9A-F]/g, '');
    return hex.length === 12 ? hex.match(/.{2}/g).join(':') : undefined;
}

/**
 * ‡πÅ‡∏õ‡∏•‡∏á timestamp ‡πÄ‡∏õ‡πá‡∏ô‡∏£‡∏π‡∏õ‡πÅ‡∏ö‡∏ö ISO 8601
 * @param {string|number} ts
 * @returns {string}
 */
function toISO(ts) {
    if (!ts) return new Date().toISOString();
    if (typeof ts === 'number') {
        const ms = ts < 1e11 ? ts * 1000 : ts; // epoch_s -> ms
        return new Date(ms).toISOString();
    }
    const d = new Date(ts);
    return isNaN(d) ? new Date().toISOString() : d.toISOString();
}

